## Project Stack (Quick Reference)

- **Training:** Google Colab Pro+ or `docker/training` (amd64) on a workstation
- **Dataset format:** COCO JSON → MDS shards (Phase B `convert_to_mds.py`) → `s3://bucket/mds/detr/vN/`
- **Model:** `microsoft/conditional-detr-resnet-50` (HuggingFace) for Round 1
- **CI/CD:** GitHub Actions — `ci_deploy.yml` exports ONNX, pushes **training** image to ECR; optional self-hosted runner for `drift_check.yml`
- **Registry:** AWS ECR — **`robops/training`** (amd64) only in this repo
- **Storage:** AWS S3 (raw images + MDS shards + weights), MongoDB Atlas optional (drift / retrain)
- **Experiment tracking:** DagsHub (MLflow + DVC remote)

## Key Data Path Conventions

- Raw images in S3: `s3://bucket/images/detr/YYYY-MM-DD/robot_id/` (legacy path; ingest may be batch-only now)
- DVC cache: `s3://bucket/dvc-cache/`
- MDS shards: `s3://bucket/mds/detr/vN/` — path in `pipeline/phase_c/detr/params.yaml`
- Holdout: `s3://bucket/data/detr/holdout/`
- Weights: `s3://bucket/weights/detr/vN/model.pt` and `model_int8.onnx`

